## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of current data and the potential bias in sources. While efforts were made to include a range of perspectives, the rapidly evolving nature of public health information means that some findings may become outdated. Additionally, the complexity of individual beliefs and cultural factors influencing vaccine hesitancy may not be fully captured in this summary. Further research, particularly qualitative studies, could provide deeper insights into the motivations behind vaccine opposition.